  "title": "🤝 Sales & Marketing (1-on-1 Mentorship)",
  "description": "<p>📍 Singapore | Full-Time | Entry-Level</p><p>We believe growth starts with guidance. Here, every team member receives <strong>1-on-1 mentorship</strong>, hands-on coaching, and continuous support from experienced leaders.</p><p>You’ll learn sales, marketing, communication, and leadership skills through real-world exposure — not theory alone.</p><p><strong>Ideal for:</strong> Coachable learners who want structured support and personal guidance.<br /><br /><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p><ul><li>📚 Willingness to learn and improve</li><li>😊 Positive, humble, and open attitude</li><li>👥 Team-oriented mindset</li></ul></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><p><ul><li>🧑‍🏫 Learn through hands-on coaching and guidance</li><li>🎯 Apply feedback in real-time campaigns</li><li>🗣 Build communication and leadership skills</li></ul></p><p><strong>Benefits</strong></p><p><ul><li>🤝 Dedicated 1-on-1 mentorship</li><li>📈 Personalised growth and development</li><li>🌟 Supportive leadership environment</li></ul></p>",
